      "location": "tokens.css (referenced but not specified)",
      "description": "Design token system is referenced throughout but no actual token values are defined. No color palette, spacing scale, or typography scale specified. Implementation cannot proceed without concrete token values.",
      "suggested_fix": "Add Section 7: Design Token System with explicit CSS custom property definitions for colors (--surface-0 through --surface-4, --text-primary/secondary/tertiary, --accent-default/hover/active), spacing (--space-1 through --space-12), typography (--font-size-xs through --font-size-2xl, --line-height-tight/normal/relaxed), and radii (--radius-sm/md/lg/full)."
    },
    {
      "severity": "high",
      "location": "Section 6 (ThemeContext)",
      "description": "ThemeContext state defined but no dark/light theme color mappings specified. Spec says 'dark default + light override' in tokens.css but provides zero actual color values. This violates the convergence criteria requiring dark mode on every screen.",
      "suggested_fix": "Define complete color palette for both themes with WCAG AA contrast ratios (4.5:1 minimum for normal text, 3:1 for large text). Include semantic color mappings for success/warning/error states in both light and dark modes."
    },
    {
      "severity": "high",
      "location": "animations.css (referenced but not specified)",
      "description": "Motion system mentioned but no actual animation durations, easing curves, or keyframe definitions provided. Spec bans 'ease/linear timing' but doesn't specify what timing functions TO use. Cannot implement consistent motion without this.",
      "suggested_fix": "Add motion token definitions: --ease-out-expo, --ease-out-quart, --duration-fast (150ms), --duration-normal (300ms), --duration-slow (500ms). Include @keyframes for skeleton shimmer, bottom-sheet slide-up, fade-in transitions."
    },
    {
      "severity": "medium",
      "location": "Section 4 (Component Architecture Map)",
      "description": "Focus visible states mentioned (':focus-visible styles apply') but no actual focus ring specifications. Premium/confident aesthetic requires precise focus ring color, width, and offset values.",
      "suggested_fix": "Specify focus ring tokens: --focus-ring-color (accent with 40% opacity), --focus-ring-width (2px), --focus-ring-offset (2px). Include reduced-motion alternative (no ring animation, instant appearance)."
    },
    {
      "severity": "medium",
      "location": "icons/status-dot.jsx",
      "description": "Colorblind support mentioned (shape variants: circle/triangle/square) but no mapping defined for which shape corresponds to which state. Implementation will be inconsistent without this.",
      "suggested_fix": "Define shape-to-state mapping: circle=success/info, triangle=warning/pending, square=error. Document in icons/README.md with SVG path specifications for each shape variant."
    },
    {
      "severity": "medium",
      "location": "Section 3 (Navigation)",
      "description": "Tab bar active state described ('accent-colored filled icon') but no actual accent color value defined. Inactive state ('--text-tertiary') also has no defined value.",
      "suggested_fix": "Add tab bar visual specs to token system: --tab-active-color, --tab-inactive-color, --tab-border-width (4px), --tab-icon-size (24px). Include hover/active states for pointer devices."
    },
    {
      "severity": "low",
      "location": "components/skeleton.jsx",
      "description": "Skeleton placeholders mentioned as 'high-fidelity' but no visual specification for shimmer animation direction, gradient stops, or animation duration.",
      "suggested_fix": "Define skeleton animation: linear gradient from --surface-2 to --surface-1 to --surface-2, animated left-to-right over 1.5s infinite loop. Match exact dimensions of final content to prevent CLS."
    }
